                        break="no" n="10"/>ραις ταῖς <rs type="institution" subtype="social_group" role="good_relations_or_behaviour" key="polis" ref="#malla"><w lemma="πόλις">πόλεσιν</w></rs> διελέγησαν μετὰ <supplied reason="lost">πάσας <w lemma="σπουδά">σπουδᾶς</w> καὶ <w lemma="φιλοτιμία">φιλοτιμίας</w></supplied>.
                          <lb n="11"/><rs type="institution" subtype="practice" role="decreeing" key="dokeo" ref="#malla"><w lemma="δοκέω">ἔδοξεν</w></rs> <placeName ref="#malla" type="ethnic"><corr>Μ</corr>αλλαίων</placeName> τοῖς <rs type="institution" subtype="board" role="decreer" key="kosmos" ref="#malla"><w lemma="κόσμος">κόσμοις</w></rs> καὶ τᾶι <rs type="institution" subtype="assembly" role="decreer" key="polis" ref="#malla"><w lemma="πόλις">πόλει</w></rs> <w lemma="ἀποκρίνω">ἀ<supplied reason="lost">ποκρίνασθαι</supplied></w>
